---
title: Roasted Pepper and Goat's Cheese Pasta with parsley and peas
description: A bowl of pasta is always a good thing, but what makes this dish really great is the array of toppings. Goat's cheese adds a beautifully creamy texture to this dish, while parsley and balsamic glaze add an element of freshness and tanginess for a meal that comes together with perfectly complementary flavours.
